                     <interp inst="t18220109-27-person289" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Wardour-street. On the 14th of December, the prisoner came to our shop, and pawned the shawl for 2 s. 6 d., in the name of 
               <persName id="t18220109-27-person290">
                  John 
                  Smith
               <interp inst="t18220109-27-person290" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
