            . I am an officer. Bassett gave me the shawl, and I took the prisoner in charge.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I left them, as my eyes would not suit the trade, which was an engraver. I was distressed, which urged me to do the crime.</p>
